('77773001-0001-4001-8001-777777773001','33330001-3333-4333-8333-333333330001','tr','Su Soğutma Kulelerinde Periyodik Bakım','su-sogutma-kulelerinde-periyodik-bakim','{\"html\": \"<section class=\\\"container mx-auto px-4 py-10\\\"><div class=\\\"max-w-3xl\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">Su Soğutma Kulelerinde Periyodik Bakım</h1><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-6\\\">Su soğutma kulelerinde verim, su kalitesi ve mekanik kondisyon birlikte yönetilmelidir. Bu rehber; saha ekibi için pratik kontrol listeleri ve önerilen periyotları bir araya getirir.</p><div class=\\\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\\\"><span class=\\\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">Bakım</span><span class=\\\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">Su Kalitesi</span><span class=\\\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">Performans</span></div></div><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">1) Görsel Kontrol</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Sızıntı, taşma, havuz seviyeleri</li><li>Anormal titreşim/ses, fan kanadı hasarı</li><li>Motor/kaplin/kayış ve bağlantı elemanları</li><li>Elektrik panosu, termik/faz koruma, kablo pabuçları</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">2) Su Kalitesi Takibi</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>pH, iletkenlik, sertlik, alkalinite</li><li>Blowdown oranı ve kimyasal şartlandırma</li><li>Biyolojik oluşum (biofilm) ve korozyon izleri</li><li>Filtre/strainer ve by-pass kontrolü</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">3) Dolgu ve Nozul Temizliği</h2><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-3\\\">Kireçlenme ve tıkanıklık, ısı transferini doğrudan düşürür. Planlı temizlik, enerji maliyetini azaltır.</p><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Nozul dağılımı: eşit yağmurlama kontrolü</li><li>Dolgu yüzeyi: tıkanıklık ve kırık parça kontrolü</li><li>Havuz: çamur/sediment temizliği</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">4) Fan – Tahrik Kontrolü</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Rulmanlar, yağlama/ısı artışı</li><li>Kayış gerginliği ve kasnak hizası</li><li>Fan balansı ve gevşek bağlantılar</li><li>Vibrasyon trendi (varsa ölçüm kayıtları)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Kısa Performans Kontrolü</h2><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-4\\\">Range/Approach değerleri sezon boyunca izlenmelidir. Ani sapmalar; su dağılımı, dolgu tıkanıklığı veya fan debisi problemlerini işaret edebilir.</p><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Giriş/çıkış su sıcaklıkları ve debi kaydı</li><li>Fan amper/enerji tüketimi trendi</li><li>Drift eliminator ve damlacık kontrolü</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Bakım Periyot Önerisi</h2><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Haftalık</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Görsel kontrol + kaçak/seviye</li><li>Panoda alarm/koruma kontrolü</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Aylık</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Nozul/filtre kontrolü</li><li>Fan tahrik ve vibrasyon gözlemi</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">3–6 Ay</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Dolgu ve havuz temizliği</li><li>Su analizi doğrulama</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Yıllık</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Kapsamlı mekanik kontrol</li><li>Performans değerlendirmesi</li></ul></div></div></div></section>\"}','Su soğutma kulelerinin verimli ve uzun ömürlü çalışması için periyodik bakım kontrol listeleri ve önerilen periyotlar.','Periyodik bakım rehberi – su soğutma kulesi ekipmanı','Su Soğutma Kulelerinde Periyodik Bakım | Ensotek','Su soğutma kulelerinde periyodik bakım: su kalitesi takibi, dolgu/nozul temizliği, fan-tahrik kontrolleri, performans izleme ve bakım periyotları.','ensotek,blog,bakim,periyodik bakım,su sogutma kuleleri,water quality,fan drive','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461'),
('77773001-0002-4002-8002-777777773001','33330001-3333-4333-8333-333333330001','en','Periodic Maintenance for Water Cooling Towers','periodic-maintenance-water-cooling-towers','{\"html\": \"<section class=\\\"container mx-auto px-4 py-10\\\"><div class=\\\"max-w-3xl\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">Periodic Maintenance for Water Cooling Towers</h1><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-6\\\">Efficiency, water quality, and mechanical condition must be managed together. This guide consolidates practical checklists and recommended intervals for field teams.</p><div class=\\\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\\\"><span class=\\\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">Maintenance</span><span class=\\\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">Water Quality</span><span class=\\\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700\\\">Performance</span></div></div><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">1) Visual Inspection</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Leaks, overflow, basin levels</li><li>Abnormal vibration/noise, fan blade damage</li><li>Motor/coupling/belt and fasteners</li><li>Electrical panel, protections, terminals</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">2) Water Quality Monitoring</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>pH, conductivity, hardness, alkalinity</li><li>Blowdown rate and chemical treatment</li><li>Biofilm and corrosion indicators</li><li>Filter/strainer and by-pass checks</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">3) Fill & Nozzle Cleaning</h2><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-3\\\">Scaling and clogging reduce heat transfer. Planned cleaning helps reduce energy costs.</p><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Nozzle distribution: uniform spray</li><li>Fill surface: clogging and damage</li><li>Basin: sludge/sediment cleaning</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">4) Fan & Drive Checks</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Bearings, lubrication and heat</li><li>Belt tension and pulley alignment</li><li>Fan balance and loose connections</li><li>Vibration trend (if available)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Quick Performance Check</h2><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-4\\\">Track Range/Approach throughout the season. Sudden deviations may indicate distribution issues, fill fouling, or fan airflow problems.</p><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Inlet/outlet water temperatures and flow logs</li><li>Fan current/energy consumption trend</li><li>Drift eliminator and droplet control</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Suggested Maintenance Frequency</h2><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Weekly</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Visual checks + levels/leaks</li><li>Panel alarms/protections</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Monthly</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Nozzle/filter inspections</li><li>Fan drive checks</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Every 3–6 months</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Basin/fill cleaning</li><li>Water analysis validation</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Annually</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Comprehensive mechanical inspection</li><li>Performance review</li></ul></div></div></div></section>\"}','Summary of periodic maintenance checklists and intervals for water cooling towers.','Periodic maintenance guide – water cooling tower equipment','Periodic Maintenance for Water Cooling Towers | Ensotek','Periodic maintenance for water cooling towers: water quality monitoring, fill/nozzle cleaning, fan-drive checks, performance tracking, and recommended intervals.','ensotek,blog,maintenance,periodic maintenance,water cooling towers,water quality,fan drive','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461'),
('77773001-0003-4003-8003-777777773001','33330001-3333-4333-8333-333333330001','de','Regelmaessige Wartung von Wasserkuehltuermen','regelmaessige-wartung-wasserkuehltuerme','{\"html\": \"<section class=\\\"container mx-auto px-4 py-10\\\"><div class=\\\"max-w-3xl\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">Regelmaessige Wartung von Wasserkuehltuermen</h1><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-6\\\">Effizienz, Wasserqualitaet und mechanischer Zustand muessen gemeinsam gesteuert werden. Dieser Leitfaden fasst praxisnahe Checklisten und Wartungsintervalle zusammen.</p></div><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">1) Sichtpruefung</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Leckagen, Ueberlauf, Beckenfuellstaende</li><li>Ungewoehnliche Vibration/Geraeusche, Ventilatorblaetter</li><li>Motor/Antrieb/Riemen und Befestigungen</li><li>Schaltschrank, Schutzfunktionen, Klemmen</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">2) Wasserqualitaet</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>pH, Leitfaehigkeit, Haerte, Alkalinitaet</li><li>Absalzung (Blowdown) und Chemiebehandlung</li><li>Biofilm und Korrosionsindikatoren</li><li>Filter/Strainer und By-pass pruefen</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">3) Fuellkoerper & Duesen</h2><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-3\\\">Verkalkung und Verstopfung reduzieren die Waermeuebertragung. Geplante Reinigung senkt Energieaufwand.</p><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Duesenbild: gleichmaessige Verteilung</li><li>Fuellkoerper: Verschmutzung und Schaeden</li><li>Becken: Schlamm/Sediment entfernen</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">4) Ventilator & Antrieb</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Lager, Schmierung und Temperatur</li><li>Riemenspannung und Riemenscheibenflucht</li><li>Ventilatorbalance und lockere Verbindungen</li><li>Vibrationstrend (falls vorhanden)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Kurzer Performance-Check</h2><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-4\\\">Range/Approach sollten saisonal getrackt werden. Plaetzliche Abweichungen deuten oft auf Verteilung, Fuellkoerper oder Luftleistung hin.</p><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Ein-/Austrittstemperaturen und Durchfluss protokollieren</li><li>Ventilatorstrom/Energieverbrauch trendbasiert beobachten</li><li>Drift Eliminator und Tropfenmitnahme kontrollieren</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Empfohlene Wartungsintervalle</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Woechentlich: Sichtpruefung + Fuellstand/Leckagen</li><li>Monatlich: Duesen/Filter + Antriebskontrolle</li><li>Alle 3–6 Monate: Becken/Fuellkoerper reinigen + Wasseranalyse validieren</li><li>Jaehrlich: umfassende mechanische Pruefung + Performance-Bewertung</li></ul></div></section>\"}','Zusammenfassung von Checklisten und Intervallen fuer die regelmaessige Wartung von Wasserkuehltuermen.','Wartungsleitfaden – Wasserkuehlturm-Anlage','Regelmaessige Wartung von Wasserkuehltuermen | Ensotek','Regelmaessige Wartung von Wasserkuehltuermen: Wasserqualitaet, Reinigung, Antriebskontrollen, Performance-Tracking und Intervalle.','ensotek,blog,wartung,regelmaessige wartung,wasserkuehltuerme,wasserqualitaet,antrieb','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461'),
('77773002-0001-4001-8001-777777773002','33330002-3333-4333-8333-333333330002','tr','Endüstriyel Tesisler için Soğutma Kulesi Yerleşimi','endustriyel-tesisler-icin-sogutma-kulesi-yerlesimi','{\"html\": \"<section class=\\\"container mx-auto px-4 py-10\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">Endüstriyel Tesisler için Soğutma Kulesi Yerleşimi</h1><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-6\\\">Doğru yerleşim; performans, gürültü, servis erişimi ve işletme sürekliliğini doğrudan etkiler. Bu yazıda proje fazında kritik yerleşim kriterlerini ve sık yapılan hataları derledik.</p><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">1) Hava Sirkülasyonu</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li><strong>Recirculation</strong> riskini azaltın; egzoz ve taze hava yollarını ayırın.</li><li>Yüksek duvarlar ve dar şaftlar, sıcak havanın geri emilmesini artırabilir.</li><li>Komşu ekipmanlardan yayılan sıcak hava ve buharı hesaba katın.</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">2) Servis ve Bakım Erişimi</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Güvenli yürüyüş yolları ve korkuluklar</li><li>Motor/fan için kaldırma alanı (vinç güzergahı)</li><li>Havuz temizliği için drenaj ve erişim planı</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">3) Gürültü Yönetimi</h2><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-4\\\">Yerleşim, gürültü kontrolünde ilk savunma hattıdır. Mesafe, bariyer ve yönlendirme doğru kurgulanırsa ek akustik yatırım azalır.</p><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Hızlı Kontroller</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>En yakın sınır/konut mesafesi</li><li>Yansıma yapan yüzeyler (duvar, cephe)</li><li>Fan hızı/kanat tipi seçimi</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Çözümler</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Akustik louver / susturucu</li><li>Ses bariyeri ve yönlendirme</li><li>VFD ile düşük devir işletme</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">4) Borulama ve Hidrolik</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Pompa–kule mesafesini minimize edin; sürtünme kayıplarını düşürün.</li><li>By-pass ve izolasyon vanalarını servis edilebilir konumda planlayın.</li><li>Drain/overflow hatlarının tahliye güvenliğini kontrol edin.</li><li>Vibrasyon izolatörleri ve esnek bağlantıları doğru seçin.</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\\\">Saha Notu</h2><p class=\\\"text-white/90\\\">Yerleşim onayından önce, 3D model veya yerleşim krokisi üzerinde bakım senaryolarını (fan-motor değişimi, dolgu temizliği, nozül servis) mutlaka simüle edin.</p></div></section>\"}','Endüstriyel tesislerde soğutma kulesi konumlandırması için hava sirkülasyonu, servis erişimi, gürültü ve hidrolik kriterleri.','Tasarım önerileri – endüstriyel tesis yerleşimi ve soğutma kulesi','Endüstriyel Tesisler için Soğutma Kulesi Yerleşimi | Ensotek','Soğutma kulesi yerleşimi: recirculation riskinin azaltılması, servis erişimi, gürültü yönetimi ve borulama/hidrolik optimizasyonu için pratik öneriler.','ensotek,blog,tesis yerlesimi,tasarim onerileri,su sogutma kuleleri,noise control,hydraulic','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461'),
('77773002-0002-4002-8002-777777773002','33330002-3333-4333-8333-333333330002','en','Cooling Tower Layout for Industrial Plants','cooling-tower-layout-industrial-plants','{\"html\": \"<section class=\\\"container mx-auto px-4 py-10\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">Cooling Tower Layout for Industrial Plants</h1><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-6\\\">Layout decisions affect performance, noise, serviceability, and uptime. This article summarizes key placement criteria and common pitfalls during the design phase.</p><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">1) Airflow Management</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Reduce <strong>recirculation</strong>; separate exhaust and fresh air paths.</li><li>High walls and narrow shafts can increase hot air re-ingestion.</li><li>Consider hot air plumes from neighboring equipment.</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">2) Service Access</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Safe walkways and guardrails</li><li>Lifting/maintenance clearance for motor and fan</li><li>Drainage plan for basin cleaning</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">3) Noise Considerations</h2><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-4\\\">Placement is the first line of defense. Proper distance, barriers, and orientation can reduce additional acoustic investments.</p><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Quick Checks</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Distance to the nearest boundary/residential area</li><li>Reflective surfaces (walls, facades)</li><li>Fan speed and blade selection</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Mitigations</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Acoustic louvers / silencers</li><li>Noise barriers and redirection</li><li>Lower-speed operation with VFD</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">4) Piping & Hydraulics</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Minimize pump-to-tower distance to reduce friction losses.</li><li>Place isolation and bypass valves for easy service.</li><li>Verify safe routing for drain/overflow lines.</li><li>Select vibration isolators and flexible connectors appropriately.</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\\\">Field Note</h2><p class=\\\"text-white/90\\\">Before final approval, simulate maintenance scenarios (fan/motor replacement, fill cleaning, nozzle service) on a layout or 3D model.</p></div></section>\"}','Practical layout guidance focusing on airflow, service access, noise, and hydraulic considerations for cooling towers in industrial plants.','Design tips – industrial plant layout and cooling tower placement','Cooling Tower Layout for Industrial Plants | Ensotek','Cooling tower layout: reduce recirculation risk, plan service access, manage noise, and optimize piping/hydraulics with practical design-phase recommendations.','ensotek,blog,plant layout,design tips,water cooling towers,noise,hydraulic','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461'),
('77773002-0003-4003-8003-777777773002','33330002-3333-4333-8333-333333330002','de','Kuehlturm-Layout fuer Industrieanlagen','kuehlturm-layout-industrieanlagen','{\"html\": \"<section class=\\\"container mx-auto px-4 py-10\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">Kuehlturm-Layout fuer Industrieanlagen</h1><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-6\\\">Layout-Entscheidungen beeinflussen Leistung, Laerm, Servicezugang und Verfuegbarkeit. Dieser Beitrag fasst zentrale Platzierungskriterien und typische Fehler in der Planungsphase zusammen.</p><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">1) Luftfuehrung</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li><strong>Recirculation</strong> vermeiden; Abluft und Frischluftwege trennen.</li><li>Hohe Waende und enge Schaechte koennen Rueckansaugung beguenstigen.</li><li>Warmluftfahnen benachbarter Anlagen beruecksichtigen.</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">2) Servicezugang</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Sichere Laufwege und Geländer</li><li>Hub-/Wartungsfreiraeume fuer Motor und Ventilator</li><li>Entwaesserungskonzept fuer Beckenreinigung</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">3) Laermmanagement</h2><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-4\\\">Die Platzierung ist die erste Schutzstufe. Distanz, Barrieren und Ausrichtung koennen akustische Zusatzmassnahmen reduzieren.</p><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Schnellchecks</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Abstand zur naechsten Grenze/Wohnbebauung</li><li>Reflektierende Flaechen (Waende/Fassaden)</li><li>Ventilatordrehzahl und Fluegelwahl</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Massnahmen</h3><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Akustik-Louver / Schalldaempfer</li><li>Laermbarrieren und Umlenkung</li><li>Niedrige Drehzahl mit Frequenzumrichter</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">4) Rohrleitungen & Hydraulik</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Pumpe–Kuehlturm Distanz minimieren; Druckverluste reduzieren.</li><li>By-pass/Absperrarmaturen servicefreundlich anordnen.</li><li>Drain/Overflow sicher ableiten.</li><li>Schwingungsdaempfer und flexible Verbindungen passend auslegen.</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\\\">Praxis-Hinweis</h2><p class=\\\"text-white/90\\\">Vor der finalen Freigabe Wartungsszenarien (Motor/Ventilator-Tausch, Fuellkoerper-Reinigung, Duesenservice) im Layout oder 3D-Modell durchspielen.</p></div></section>\"}','Kompakte Layout-Empfehlungen: Luftfuehrung, Servicezugang, Laerm und Hydraulik fuer Kuehltuerme in Industrieanlagen.','Design-Tipps – Anlagenlayout und Kuehlturm-Positionierung','Kuehlturm-Layout fuer Industrieanlagen | Ensotek','Kuehlturm-Layout: Recirculation reduzieren, Servicezugang planen, Laerm managen und Rohrleitung/Hydraulik optimieren.','ensotek,blog,anlagenlayout,design tipps,wasserkuehltuerme,laerm,hydraulik','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461'),
('77773101-0001-4001-8001-777777773101','33331001-3333-4333-8333-333333331001','tr','FRP Soğutma Kulelerinde Isı Transferi Temelleri','frp-sogutma-kulelerinde-isi-transferi-temelleri','{\"html\": \"<section class=\\\"container mx-auto px-4 py-10\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">FRP Soğutma Kulelerinde Isı Transferi Temelleri</h1><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-6\\\">Isı transferi performansı; hava debisi, dolgu (fill) verimi ve su dağıtım kararlılığı ile doğrudan ilişkilidir. Bu yazıda temel metrikleri (range/approach), sık sahaya yansıyan problemleri ve hızlı teşhis ipuçlarını özetliyoruz.</p><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Temel Kavramlar</h2><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Range</h3><p class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\">Kule giriş ve çıkış su sıcaklığı farkı. Sistem yükünü ve kule kapasite kullanımını anlamaya yardımcı olur.</p></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Approach</h3><p class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\">Kule çıkış su sıcaklığı ile yaş termometre (wet-bulb) arasındaki fark. Ne kadar düşükse performans o kadar iyidir.</p></div></div></div><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">1) Hava Debisi</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Fan hızı (VFD), kanat açısı ve kanat yüzeyi</li><li>Hava girişlerinde tıkanıklık ve louver durumu</li><li>Recirculation ve kısa devre hava akışı</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">2) Dolgu Verimi</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Dolgu yüzey alanı ve temas süresi</li><li>Kireçlenme / biyolojik oluşum (biofouling)</li><li>Yanlış kimyasal şartlandırma kaynaklı tıkanma</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Hızlı Teşhis Tablosu</h2><div class=\\\"overflow-x-auto\\\"><table class=\\\"w-full text-left border-collapse\\\"><thead><tr class=\\\"text-slate-900\\\"><th class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-200\\\">Belirti</th><th class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-200\\\">Muhtemel Neden</th><th class=\\\"py-2 border-b border-slate-200\\\">Kontrol</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\"><tr><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Approach yükseldi</td><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Dolgu kirli / hava debisi düşük</td><td class=\\\"py-2 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Dolgu/nozul + fan amper</td></tr><tr><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Range düştü</td><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Yük azaldı / debi değişti</td><td class=\\\"py-2 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Debi ölçümü + proses</td></tr><tr><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Damlacık artışı</td><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Drift eliminator hasarı</td><td class=\\\"py-2 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Eliminator kontrolü</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\\\">Pratik Öneri</h2><p class=\\\"text-white/90\\\">Trend analizi yapın: aynı hava koşullarında (benzer wet-bulb) approach/range ve fan enerji tüketimini kaydedin. Sapmalar, arıza oluşmadan önce sinyal verir.</p></div></section>\"}','FRP soğutma kulelerinde ısı transferini etkileyen temel parametreler: range/approach, hava debisi, dolgu verimi ve hızlı teşhis ipuçları.','Teknik rehber – FRP soğutma kulelerinde ısı transferi','FRP Soğutma Kulelerinde Isı Transferi Temelleri | Ensotek','FRP soğutma kulelerinde ısı transferi: range/approach metrikleri, fan hava debisi, dolgu verimi, su dağıtımı ve saha için hızlı teşhis kontrol listeleri.','ensotek,blog,frp,isi transferi,teknik rehber,su sogutma kuleleri,approach,range','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461'),
('77773101-0002-4002-8002-777777773101','33331001-3333-4333-8333-333333331001','en','Basics of Heat Transfer in FRP Cooling Towers','basics-heat-transfer-frp-cooling-towers','{\"html\": \"<section class=\\\"container mx-auto px-4 py-10\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">Basics of Heat Transfer in FRP Cooling Towers</h1><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-6\\\">Heat transfer performance depends on airflow, fill efficiency, and stable water distribution. This article summarizes key metrics (range/approach), common site issues, and quick troubleshooting tips.</p><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Core Metrics</h2><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Range</h3><p class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\">Difference between inlet and outlet water temperature. Indicates load and capacity utilization.</p></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Approach</h3><p class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\">Difference between outlet water temperature and wet-bulb. Lower approach typically means better performance.</p></div></div></div><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">1) Airflow</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Fan speed (VFD), blade angle and surface condition</li><li>Blockage at air inlets and louver condition</li><li>Recirculation and short-circuit airflow</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">2) Fill Efficiency</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Surface area and contact time</li><li>Scaling and biofouling</li><li>Fouling due to inconsistent water treatment</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Quick Troubleshooting</h2><div class=\\\"overflow-x-auto\\\"><table class=\\\"w-full text-left border-collapse\\\"><thead><tr class=\\\"text-slate-900\\\"><th class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-200\\\">Symptom</th><th class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-200\\\">Likely cause</th><th class=\\\"py-2 border-b border-slate-200\\\">Check</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\"><tr><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Approach increases</td><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Fouled fill / low airflow</td><td class=\\\"py-2 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Fill/nozzles + fan current</td></tr><tr><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Range decreases</td><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Load/flow change</td><td class=\\\"py-2 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Flow measurement + process</td></tr><tr><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">More droplet carryover</td><td class=\\\"py-2 pr-4 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Damaged drift eliminator</td><td class=\\\"py-2 border-b border-slate-100\\\">Eliminator inspection</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\\\"bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\\\">Practical Tip</h2><p class=\\\"text-white/90\\\">Track trends: at similar wet-bulb conditions, record approach/range and fan energy. Deviations are early-warning signals.</p></div></section>\"}','Key parameters for heat transfer in FRP cooling towers: range/approach, airflow, fill efficiency, and quick troubleshooting.','Technical guide – heat transfer in FRP cooling towers','Basics of Heat Transfer in FRP Cooling Towers | Ensotek','Heat transfer in FRP cooling towers: range/approach metrics, fan airflow, fill efficiency, water distribution, and quick field troubleshooting checklists.','ensotek,blog,frp,heat transfer,technical guide,water cooling towers,approach,range','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461','2026-01-02 03:32:22.461'),
('77773101-0003-4003-8003-777777773101','33331001-3333-4333-8333-333333331001','de','Grundlagen der Waermeuebertragung in FRP-Kuehltuermen','grundlagen-waermeuebertragung-frp-kuehltuerme','{\"html\": \"<section class=\\\"container mx-auto px-4 py-10\\\"><h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">Grundlagen der Waermeuebertragung in FRP-Kuehltuermen</h1><p class=\\\"text-slate-700 mb-6\\\">Die Leistung haengt von Luftstrom, Fuellkoerper (Fill) und stabiler Wasserverteilung ab. Hier fassen wir Kennzahlen (Range/Approach), typische Praxisprobleme und schnelle Diagnosehinweise zusammen.</p><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">Grundbegriffe</h2><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Range</h3><p class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\">Differenz zwischen Ein- und Austrittstemperatur des Wassers. Zeigt Last und Auslastung.</p></div><div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-5\\\"><h3 class=\\\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2\\\">Approach</h3><p class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\">Differenz zwischen Austrittswasser und Nasskugeltemperatur. Ein kleiner Approach bedeutet meist bessere Performance.</p></div></div></div><div class=\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">1) Luftleistung</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2\\\"><li>Ventilatordrehzahl (FU), Schaufelwinkel, Zustand</li><li>Einlassbereiche, Louver und Verstopfungen</li><li>Recirculation und Kurzschlussstroemung</li></ul></div><div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6\\\"><h2 class=\\\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3\\\">2) Fuellkoerper-Effizienz</h2><ul class=\\\"list-disc pl-6 text-sl