('22221506-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbb1506en03','bbbb1506-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1506','en','Is maintenance easy?','Yes. The design allows easy removal/installation for cleaning and maintenance.',30,1,'2026-01-02 03:32:20.837','2026-01-02 03:32:20.837'),
