('22221508-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-bbbb1508tr03','bbbb1508-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1508','tr','Montaj tipi nasıldır?','Modüler kasetler halinde, boşluksuz şekilde monte edilerek tüm kesit kapatılır.',30,1,'2026-01-02 03:32:20.903','2026-01-02 03:32:20.903'),
('22221508-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbb1508en01','bbbb1508-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1508','en','What do drift eliminators do?','They reduce water droplet carryover to the atmosphere and help prevent water loss.',10,1,'2026-01-02 03:32:20.910','2026-01-02 03:32:20.910'),
('22221508-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbb1508en02','bbbb1508-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1508','en','Where are they installed?','Between the fan deck platform and the water distribution system inside the tower.',20,1,'2026-01-02 03:32:20.910','2026-01-02 03:32:20.910'),
('22221508-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbb1508en03','bbbb1508-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1508','en','How are they mounted?','As modular cassette blocks mounted without gaps to cover the full cross-section.',30,1,'2026-01-02 03:32:20.910','2026-01-02 03:32:20.910'),
