('22221510-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbb1510en03','bbbb1510-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1510','en','Is it reusable after cleaning?','Yes. It can be washed and reused, reducing maintenance and replacement costs.',30,1,'2026-01-02 03:32:20.981','2026-01-02 03:32:20.981'),
